p: In the District Court holding terms at Seattle.
In Re Lee Kee Peitition for writ of Habeas Corpus. No. 4444.

I, J H McGraw, Sheriff of King County W.T. do hereby certify that on the 1st day of June 1885, at Seattle, in said King County, I served the writ of Habeas Corpus issued by the above entitled anetter, a copy of which is hereto affixed upon James H Wolley, Chief of Police of the City of Seattle, by delivering the same to him personally, at said City of Seattle, in said County
Dated at Seattle the 1st day of June 1885. J H McGraw Sheriff
Sheriff's Fees: Service 1.00 Copy .40 Travel 20 Certificate .50 .70 $2.10
